thread.title_full: PartsGeek reviewed by Joseph r Leal

author: Joseph r Leal
title: Joseph r Leal
text: Customer service is on point. The guys are very professional and the are very knowledgeable. I am a woman who don't know much about cars and they make it so easy. Prices are pretty good too. Love the timely manner in which my order is shipped to me. I will always check Parts Geek when making purchases for my car before shopping anywhere else. Maria Leal
